Eden Hazard is favourite to win PFA Player of the Year at the 42nd PFA Awards in London on Sunday . 
  Tottenham striker Harry Kane is also nominated for Young Player of Year and Philippe Coutinho for Liverpool . 
  David de Gea and Frank Lampard Snr arrived at the Grosvenor House in Mayfair . 
  Liverpool captain Steven Gerrard and Kolo Toure also in attendance . 
  Chelsea striker Eden Hazard is the favourite for the award . 
 